verbose_text: Previous studies have reported that Sry transgenic constructs without the glutamine rich domain fail to cause sex reversal in mice with the XX karyotype XREF_BIBR, mutations in either NLS cause XY sex reversal in humans XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR and most cases of human XY sex reversal involve mutations in HMG box.
